OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be windy with blustery
OL,6,Fshowers, these heavy at times with
OL,7,Frisk of hail and the odd rumble of
OL,8,Fthunder. Bright with occasional sunny
OL,9,Fspells and feeling chilly in the
OL,10,Fstrong to gale force west or northwest
OL,11,Fwinds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FThe winds easing and the
OL,14,Fshowers becoming well scattered this
OL,15,Fevening. Dry of a time overnight, but
OL,16,Fthickening cloud and patchy rain later
OL,17,Fas winds turn into the southwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
