OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FRather cloudy with patchy
OL,6,Flight rain and drizzle at first, but
OL,7,Fbecoming mostly dry. Best of any
OL,8,Fbrightness across Orkney. Moderate to
OL,9,Ffresh southwest winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,12,FOutbreaks of rain gradually clearing
OL,13,Fsouth on Wednesday and windy at times.
OL,14,FThen mainly dry on Thursday and Friday
OL,15,Fwith some bright or sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
